<template>
  <header class="header-wrap">
    <button type="button" @click="sidebarToggle">ToggleSideBar</button>
  </header>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      isActive: false
    }
  },
  methods: {
    sidebarToggle (){
      // document.querySelector('body').classList.toggle('sidebarClose')
      this.$emit('btnTest', this.isActive)
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
